# Poem of the Day - Project Structure Guide

## Overview
This is a Swift iOS app called "Poem of the Day" with comprehensive widget support and extensive testing coverage.

## Main Architecture
- **MVVM Pattern**: ViewModels manage business logic, Views handle UI
- **Dependency Injection**: Uses [DependencyContainer.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Core/DependencyContainer.swift)
- **Protocol-Oriented**: Core protocols defined in [Protocols.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Core/Protocols.swift)
- **SwiftUI**: Modern declarative UI framework

## Key Entry Points
- **Main App**: [Poem_of_the_DayApp.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Poem_of_the_DayApp.swift)
- **Main View**: [ContentView.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Views/Screens/ContentView.swift)
- **Widget Bundle**: [Poem_of_the_Day_WidgetBundle.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day Widget/Poem_of_the_Day_WidgetBundle.swift)

## Core Components

### Models
- [Poem.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Models/Poem.swift) - Main poem data structure
- [VibeModels.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Models/VibeModels.swift) - Vibe analysis models
- [PoemError.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Models/PoemError.swift) - Error handling
- [PoemHistoryEntry.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Models/PoemHistoryEntry.swift) - History tracking

### ViewModels
- [PoemViewModel.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/ViewModels/PoemViewModel.swift) - Main poem display logic
- [PoemHistoryViewModel.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/ViewModels/PoemHistoryViewModel.swift) - History management

### Services
- [NetworkService.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Services/NetworkService.swift) - HTTP networking
- [PoemGenerationService.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Services/PoemGenerationService.swift) - AI poem generation
- [PoemRepository.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Services/PoemRepository.swift) - Data persistence
- [VibeAnalyzer.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Services/VibeAnalyzer.swift) - Mood analysis
- [TelemetryService.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Services/TelemetryService.swift) - Analytics

### Configuration
- [AppConfiguration.swift](mdc:Poem of the Day/Core/AppConfiguration.swift) - App settings
- [RSSFeeds.json](mdc:Poem of the Day/Poem of the Day/RSSFeeds.json) - RSS feed sources
- [VibeKeywords.json](mdc:Poem of the Day/Poem of the Day/VibeKeywords.json) - Mood keywords

## Testing Structure
- **Unit Tests**: `Poem of the DayTests/` - Comprehensive service and model tests
- **UI Tests**: `Poem of the DayUITests/` - End-to-end user interface tests
- **Integration Tests**: Full workflow testing
- **Performance Tests**: Memory and speed optimization validation

## Widget Extension
Separate target with shared models and services for iOS widgets and Live Activities.
